The '''Agrarian Party''' ({{lang-tg|Ҳизби аграрии Тоҷикистон}} ''Hizbi Agrarii Tojikiston'', {{lang-fa|حزب اگرری تاجیکستان}}) is a [[political party]] in [[Tajikistan]]. The chief of the APT is [[Amir Burievich Qaroqulov]].<ref>https://www.state.gov/r/pa/ei/bgn/5775.htm US DoS Tajikistan Profile October 2009</ref>  The Agrarian Party of Tajikistan has nominated 22 candidates for parliamentary elections scheduled for 28 February 2010.

